channel.title: Whats a good way to beat up your wife?
channel.description:
Hey sorry if this is in the wrong section but my latest "Wife" is cooking my dinner cold as shit.

So if somebody wants to close this by all means go for your life, but there's not a chance in hell you'll ever make me close my legs.
- Mark Gerhard
